Notes: Declined for duty time at 0215.  Proposed mission was for KBGR-KCAR-KPWM-KBGR.  While planning spreadsheet listed 0335 as a wheels-up cutoff for this mission, two recent historical examples of this itinerary were located each comprising 4.5 hrs of total mission time, which would suggest a wheels-up cutoff of 0230.  At 0215, the crew was still finishing with a previous call at EMMC and the aircraft was still being fueled, making wheels-up at 0230 impossible.  I offered the alternatives of mission acceptance if a patient rendezvous could be arranged in KCAR or if the destination could be changed to KBGR, but the request was withdrawn, presumably because these could not be accomplished.
